 Editor's note: The headline has been edited to reflect that Makhosi Khoza hit out at the ANC leadership. JOHANNESBURG - ANC MP Makhosi Khoza has hit out at the party s leadership, accusing it of arrogance and empowering the opposition.Khoza wrote a hard-hitting Facebook post, expressing her concerns.She says political patronage has claimed the sanity of the ANC leadership.Khoza says the governing party's story has turned tragic by handing power over to the DA and EFF.She believes that Friday's anti-Zuma protests are definitive signs of her party's poor leadership.Khoza says the ANC is destroying itself, while the majority remains trapped in poverty, unemployment and inequality.eNCA